# Deployment & Operations

## Build & Development
- **pnpm** - Use pnpm for package management (version 9.0.0)
- **Turborepo** - Use turbo for build orchestration
- **Node.js** - Require Node.js >= 18
- **TypeScript** - Use TypeScript 5.8+ with strict mode

## Development Commands
```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm i

# Start development
pnpm dev

# Build all packages
pnpm build

# Lint all packages
pnpm lint

# Type check
pnpm check-types

# Format code
pnpm format
```

## Deployment Targets
- **Mobile**: Expo EAS Build for iOS/Android
- **Web Business**: Cloudflare Workers via Wrangler
- **Web Consumer**: Cloudflare Workers via Wrangler  
- **Web Landing**: Cloudflare Workers via Wrangler
- **Backend**: Convex cloud deployment

## Environment Management
- **Environment files** - Use .env.local for local development
- **Secrets** - Store secrets in environment variables
- **Configuration** - Use wrangler.jsonc for Cloudflare config
- **Build optimization** - Use Vite for fast builds

## CI/CD Patterns
- **Automated testing** - Run tests on every PR
- **Type checking** - Ensure TypeScript compilation
- **Linting** - Enforce code quality standards
- **Security scanning** - Check for vulnerabilities

## Monitoring & Observability
- **Error tracking** - Monitor application errors
- **Performance monitoring** - Track app performance
